1
00:00:01,110 --> 00:00:03,710
(Episode 48)

2
00:00:03,780 --> 00:00:07,180
(Suk Hee's Side Dishes)

3
00:00:11,720 --> 00:00:13,350
Let's go see how a normal person lives.

4
00:00:15,320 --> 00:00:16,420
This should be fun.

5
00:00:17,220 --> 00:00:21,360
From now on, I'm not Ma Seo Rin.
I'm Oh Jang Mi.

6
00:00:26,500 --> 00:00:29,930
Wearing glasses after getting LASEK
is making me dizzy.

7
00:00:43,720 --> 00:00:44,750
Shit.

8
00:00:45,280 --> 00:00:47,450
What is that smell? Gross.

9
00:00:49,020 --> 00:00:52,660
Jang Mi's home.
Jang Mi loves fermented soybean stew.

10
00:00:53,490 --> 00:00:54,960
Jang Mi is so pretty.

11
00:00:56,130 --> 00:00:57,260
Fermented soybean stew?

12
00:01:04,300 --> 00:01:05,300
Oh, right.

13
00:01:11,380 --> 00:01:13,750
You're little angels, my absolute angels.

14
00:01:14,350 --> 00:01:17,280
So beautiful, my daughters.

15
00:01:17,520 --> 00:01:19,480
Ok Hee, Tok Hee.

16
00:01:22,820 --> 00:01:24,160
Tok Hee...

17
00:01:27,290 --> 00:01:28,290
It's Tok Hee!

18
00:01:29,990 --> 00:01:32,560
You're not Jang Mi! You're Tok Hee!

19
00:01:32,700 --> 00:01:34,100
Tok Hee's here!

20
00:01:35,200 --> 00:01:38,300
What? Does she know I'm not Oh Jang Mi?

21
00:01:38,570 --> 00:01:39,770
How?

22
00:01:44,680 --> 00:01:45,780
My sweet Tok Hee.

23
00:01:47,050 --> 00:01:48,180
Tok Hee is pretty.

24
00:01:48,780 --> 00:01:49,980
My sweet Tok Hee.

25
00:01:50,780 --> 00:01:53,120
Do you really know who I am?

26
00:01:53,550 --> 00:01:56,890
My Tok Hee is back from her picnic.

27
00:02:00,490 --> 00:02:02,360
I missed you, Tok Hee.

28
00:02:03,600 --> 00:02:05,430
Tok Hee is Suk Hee's daughter.

29
00:02:06,230 --> 00:02:09,170
Jang Mi is pretty. Tok Hee is pretty.

30
00:02:10,270 --> 00:02:12,500
You're my daughter, Suk Hee's daughter.

31
00:02:21,210 --> 00:02:24,220
No, this can't be happening.

32
00:02:24,220 --> 00:02:25,480
Tok Hee is pretty.

33
00:02:26,420 --> 00:02:27,990
Tok Hee is my daughter.

34
00:02:36,330 --> 00:02:37,330
Mom.

35
00:02:38,160 --> 00:02:39,160
Mom?

36
00:02:42,670 --> 00:02:43,740
Mom.

37
00:02:48,410 --> 00:02:50,540
What do I do?

38
00:02:57,120 --> 00:02:58,120
Whatever.

39
00:02:59,720 --> 00:03:01,050
If I get caught, so be it.

40
00:03:13,260 --> 00:03:16,270
(Ma Dae Chang)

41
00:03:17,340 --> 00:03:18,740
"Ma Dae Chang?"

42
00:03:19,970 --> 00:03:21,570
That name sounds familiar.

43
00:03:23,310 --> 00:03:24,710
What? Wait a second.

44
00:03:25,740 --> 00:03:27,850
Seo Rin's full name is Ma Seo Rin?

45
00:04:02,110 --> 00:04:04,480
Seo Rin, are you just getting home?

46
00:04:05,850 --> 00:04:07,590
Is that my grandfather?

47
00:04:08,090 --> 00:04:10,290
Why did you ring the doorbell
instead of using the code?

48
00:04:10,960 --> 00:04:12,860
- Have you been drinking?
- What?

49
00:04:13,630 --> 00:04:14,730
Well...

50
00:04:19,300 --> 00:04:21,130
Is she Seo Rin's mom?

51
00:04:21,930 --> 00:04:24,340
Why are you just standing there, Seo Rin?

52
00:04:25,600 --> 00:04:26,900
Right.

53
00:04:40,390 --> 00:04:41,390
My goodness.

54
00:04:41,390 --> 00:04:43,390
What did Seo Rin just say?

55
00:04:43,450 --> 00:04:47,330
I asked if she'd been drinking.
I think she's just messing with me.

56
00:04:56,970 --> 00:04:58,270
Don't get caught.

57
00:04:59,440 --> 00:05:02,010
My room is on the second floor,
all the way to the right.

58
00:05:03,610 --> 00:05:06,080
She said the last one on the right.

59
00:05:18,520 --> 00:05:21,330
This is next-level difficult.

60
00:05:22,430 --> 00:05:24,930
I finally made it into Seo Rin's room.

61
00:05:28,530 --> 00:05:30,400
It's a total princess room.

62
00:05:34,010 --> 00:05:35,040
Do you want me to get dinner ready?

63
00:05:35,640 --> 00:05:37,780
Your mom's coming home soon.
What do you want to do?

64
00:05:39,040 --> 00:05:40,110
Do you want to wait and eat with her?

65
00:05:40,480 --> 00:05:41,480
With Mom?

66
00:05:42,250 --> 00:05:43,250
No, thank you.

67
00:05:43,510 --> 00:05:46,450
- What?
- I mean, I already ate.

68
00:05:57,900 --> 00:06:00,000
So she's not Seo Rin's mom.

69
00:06:01,170 --> 00:06:03,470
Then who's the one who raised Seo Rin?

70
00:06:04,040 --> 00:06:05,970
That person has to know.

71
00:06:06,540 --> 00:06:08,940
Why Seo Rin and I were separated.

72
00:06:10,780 --> 00:06:13,710
Anyway, I wonder how Seo Rin's doing.

73
00:06:17,180 --> 00:06:18,180
I'm so dizzy.

74
00:06:28,360 --> 00:06:31,730
Oh Jang Mi, where have you been all day?

75
00:06:33,660 --> 00:06:34,730
Here, trim these.

76
00:06:36,970 --> 00:06:37,970
What?

77
00:06:40,070 --> 00:06:41,710
You want me to trim these?

78
00:06:41,870 --> 00:06:44,180
What's with you?
Why are you acting so surprised?

79
00:06:44,510 --> 00:06:47,880
What? She expects me
to trim these stupid bean sprouts?

80
00:06:48,110 --> 00:06:49,150
Hey, Oh Jang Mi.

81
00:06:49,450 --> 00:06:51,680
We open early tomorrow,

82
00:06:51,680 --> 00:06:53,720
so don't complain
and get the side dishes made.

83
00:06:53,850 --> 00:06:54,850
Got it?

84
00:06:54,850 --> 00:06:55,920
Shit.

85
00:06:56,420 --> 00:06:58,160
I can't do it. Whatever.

86
00:06:59,260 --> 00:07:00,320
I won't do it!

87
00:07:01,490 --> 00:07:02,560
Hey, Oh Jang Mi!

88
00:07:03,800 --> 00:07:06,930
What's gotten into her all of a sudden?

89
00:07:09,570 --> 00:07:10,700
Shit.

90
00:07:10,700 --> 00:07:12,240
She wants me to do what?

91
00:07:12,240 --> 00:07:13,840
I don't know how to do that stuff.

92
00:07:14,010 --> 00:07:15,140
Oh Jang Mi,

93
00:07:15,140 --> 00:07:17,240
Tae Sook is in a foul mood today,
so don't get on her nerves.

94
00:07:17,710 --> 00:07:21,480
Is this guy Jang Mi's brother?
Then was that woman earlier her sister?

95
00:07:21,950 --> 00:07:23,920
She seemed just like
one of the evil stepsisters.

96
00:07:26,820 --> 00:07:28,550
- Jang Mi.
- Hey.

97
00:07:28,720 --> 00:07:32,460
Darn it. What now?
I have no idea what to do.

98
00:07:32,920 --> 00:07:34,130
I just want to hide.

99
00:07:34,130 --> 00:07:36,330
Did you already hear from Tae Sook?

100
00:07:36,930 --> 00:07:39,130
Kang Baek Ho, what did my sister say?

101
00:07:39,530 --> 00:07:40,530
What?

102
00:07:41,200 --> 00:07:43,170
Well, he is pretty handsome.

103
00:07:43,670 --> 00:07:46,270
Not my type, but definitely Oh Jang Mi's.

104
00:07:47,510 --> 00:07:50,310
I think it's time to make a run for it.

105
00:07:51,640 --> 00:07:54,550
- Hey, Jang Mi.
- Hey, I asked you what she said.

106
00:07:54,810 --> 00:07:55,810
Kang Baek Ho.

107
00:07:56,410 --> 00:07:57,420
Tell me.

108
00:07:58,880 --> 00:08:00,620
Ask Tae Sook.

109
00:08:05,690 --> 00:08:06,960
Gosh, seriously.

110
00:08:08,460 --> 00:08:09,560
Hey, Oh Jang Mi.

111
00:08:10,430 --> 00:08:11,430
Darn it.

112
00:08:13,430 --> 00:08:16,470
My gosh, Oh Jang Mi. Why are you crying?

113
00:08:17,400 --> 00:08:19,540
So this is what it's like
for a normal person.

114
00:08:20,070 --> 00:08:22,270
What do you mean? Why are you crying?

115
00:08:22,340 --> 00:08:24,010
Mind your own business!

116
00:08:24,110 --> 00:08:25,840
What's gotten into you all of a sudden?

117
00:08:27,750 --> 00:08:28,950
Just hurry up and trim these.

118
00:08:31,080 --> 00:08:33,950
Shit. How am I even supposed
to trim these?

119
00:08:48,170 --> 00:08:49,700
What do you think you're doing?

120
00:08:50,800 --> 00:08:52,570
Are you staging a protest against me?

121
00:08:52,770 --> 00:08:54,710
If you have a problem, use your words.

122
00:08:57,880 --> 00:09:00,140
Tae Sook, tell me the truth.

123
00:09:00,480 --> 00:09:02,980
Kang Baek Ho told me to ask you.
What is it?

124
00:09:03,110 --> 00:09:05,250
Oh Jang Mi, you know what's going on,
don't you?

125
00:09:05,620 --> 00:09:06,880
And that's why you're protesting.

126
00:09:12,060 --> 00:09:14,030
Yes, you got it.

127
00:09:14,590 --> 00:09:17,660
Tae Sook,
did you accept the settlement money?

128
00:09:18,000 --> 00:09:22,030
- Yes, I did!
- How could you accept that?

129
00:09:22,100 --> 00:09:25,400
Stop it. You're scaring Tok Hee.

130
00:09:26,600 --> 00:09:28,970
What was I supposed to do?
The rent is overdue.

131
00:09:29,040 --> 00:09:31,680
- Should we sit around and get evicted?
- Are you crazy?

132
00:09:32,140 --> 00:09:34,180
You traded Dad's life for just money?

133
00:09:34,180 --> 00:09:35,480
And you think you did the right thing?

134
00:09:35,550 --> 00:09:38,750
"Dad's life?" Don't be so dramatic!

135
00:09:38,980 --> 00:09:41,220
And what was that? "Just money?"

136
00:09:41,920 --> 00:09:44,490
Have you ever earned that kind of cash?

137
00:09:44,560 --> 00:09:46,090
How dare you look down on it?

138
00:09:46,860 --> 00:09:47,990
Are you done talking?

139
00:09:49,830 --> 00:09:51,560
You think I'm not making money
because I don't want to?

140
00:09:52,160 --> 00:09:54,600
Do you have any right to say that to me?

141
00:09:54,800 --> 00:09:56,900
Think about everything you've done.

142
00:09:57,030 --> 00:10:00,070
- All the grief you've given Dad!
- Hey, Oh Tae Pyung!

143
00:10:01,540 --> 00:10:04,280
Please, stop. Tok Hee is scared.

144
00:10:04,540 --> 00:10:05,880
Tok Hee is afraid.

145
00:10:06,910 --> 00:10:08,980
Tok Hee's ears hurt.

146
00:10:13,680 --> 00:10:14,890
Mom?

147
00:10:16,420 --> 00:10:17,420
Mom.

148
00:10:18,890 --> 00:10:19,960
My mom.

149
00:10:28,300 --> 00:10:30,470
What's taking Seo Rin's mom so long?

150
00:10:32,200 --> 00:10:34,070
Seo Rin said she had proof.

151
00:10:34,970 --> 00:10:36,370
I wonder where she put it.

152
00:11:13,680 --> 00:11:14,680
Right.

153
00:11:15,650 --> 00:11:17,620
She really is the twin
my mother gave birth to.

154
00:11:19,820 --> 00:11:23,220
So who is Seo Rin's mom, anyway?

155
00:11:34,100 --> 00:11:36,900
- I'm home.
- Are we invisible to you?

156
00:11:40,040 --> 00:11:43,540
Why was Seo Rin left
sitting outside for 30 minutes?

157
00:11:43,810 --> 00:11:45,540
What? Seo Rin was?

158
00:11:46,140 --> 00:11:47,850
Why was she sitting outside?

159
00:11:47,950 --> 00:11:51,520
- She was probably just drunk.
- Jin Hong Ju, that's exactly it.

160
00:11:53,050 --> 00:11:54,890
Ma Dae Chang.

161
00:11:55,950 --> 00:11:58,620
Wait, who was that again?
I've heard that name so many times.

162
00:12:00,020 --> 00:12:01,560
Ma Dae Chang?

163
00:12:03,130 --> 00:12:05,260
Her grandfather is the chairman
of Dream Group?

164
00:12:09,270 --> 00:12:12,270
Why would Seo Rin want
to ever rush home...

165
00:12:12,570 --> 00:12:14,470
when the house is crawling
with all these freeloaders?

166
00:12:14,570 --> 00:12:17,040
Watch your mouth.
What makes you think we're freeloaders?

167
00:12:17,110 --> 00:12:19,640
You're not?
Then what exactly is your place here?

168
00:12:20,110 --> 00:12:21,250
Know your place.

169
00:12:21,310 --> 00:12:23,150
That's no way to speak
to your mother-in-law.

170
00:12:23,210 --> 00:12:24,780
Mother-in-law?
What are you talking about, Father?

171
00:12:25,050 --> 00:12:26,980
Did you two get married? Is it official?

172
00:12:27,120 --> 00:12:29,120
I told you not to treat
her that way, regardless!

173
00:12:30,290 --> 00:12:31,360
I'm sorry, Father.

174
00:12:31,960 --> 00:12:33,760
But I'm at my wits' end.

175
00:12:34,330 --> 00:12:35,430
Seo Rin...

176
00:12:35,860 --> 00:12:38,730
was sitting outside the house
for 30 whole minutes.

177
00:12:38,900 --> 00:12:40,900
What? How did she know that?

178
00:12:41,300 --> 00:12:42,970
Could that be Seo Rin's mom?

179
00:12:43,200 --> 00:12:45,940
Seo Rin is your one
and only blood relative.

180
00:12:46,900 --> 00:12:47,910
Which means,

181
00:12:48,510 --> 00:12:50,070
it's because of the freeloaders...

182
00:12:50,340 --> 00:12:52,640
she can't stand facing every day.

183
00:12:57,410 --> 00:12:59,750
What? CEO Chae Hwa Young...

184
00:13:00,320 --> 00:13:01,990
is Seo Rin's mother?

185
00:13:02,720 --> 00:13:03,890
No way.

186
00:13:03,990 --> 00:13:07,420
How can Seo Rin's mom be CEO Chae?

187
00:13:08,560 --> 00:13:11,030
No, it can't be true.

188
00:13:12,160 --> 00:13:15,070
You've really got some nerve.
Are you finished?

189
00:13:15,400 --> 00:13:18,570
How can you be so sure
that's why she's upset?

190
00:13:18,770 --> 00:13:21,710
- Seo Rin and I got along just fine.
- Is that what Seo Rin said?

191
00:13:22,070 --> 00:13:23,870
Or is this just a story you made up?

192
00:13:23,940 --> 00:13:25,240
Why would I make something like that up?

193
00:13:26,210 --> 00:13:28,350
And the fact that Seo Rin's been drinking
every day...

194
00:13:28,950 --> 00:13:30,680
is because she's having such a hard time.

195
00:13:36,690 --> 00:13:38,520
I can't believe CEO Chae
is Seo Rin's mother.

196
00:13:39,690 --> 00:13:41,590
But CEO Chae already knew who I was.

197
00:13:42,290 --> 00:13:46,130
That means she must have known
Seo Rin and I are twins all along.

198
00:13:49,830 --> 00:13:50,830
Seo Rin.

199
00:13:53,040 --> 00:13:54,040
Wait, you...

200
00:14:01,980 --> 00:14:05,320
She did whatever she could
to keep me and Seo Rin from meeting.

201
00:14:05,680 --> 00:14:08,350
I'd like to send you abroad to study.

202
00:14:08,990 --> 00:14:10,090
Study abroad?

203
00:14:14,490 --> 00:14:15,630
Jang Mi!

204
00:14:16,430 --> 00:14:18,560
Jang Mi, my stomach hurts...

205
00:14:18,630 --> 00:14:22,600
But I have to go
to my interview right now.

206
00:14:24,770 --> 00:14:27,140
- CEO Chae!
- Take me to the hospital!

207
00:14:32,540 --> 00:14:34,680
Don't you get that
Dad's death was suspicious?

208
00:14:35,210 --> 00:14:37,310
Everything about it is suspicious,
and nothing's been solved.

209
00:14:37,380 --> 00:14:39,080
So how could you sign
those settlement papers!

210
00:14:39,080 --> 00:14:40,780
That's enough, Oh Tae Pyung!

211
00:14:40,990 --> 00:14:42,790
Jang Mi, you tell me.

212
00:14:43,490 --> 00:14:45,460
Can you understand
why she would sign those papers?

213
00:14:48,930 --> 00:14:51,730
The dead are gone.
The living have to move on.

214
00:14:51,960 --> 00:14:54,630
And it's not like she got nothing.
She took the money, right?

215
00:14:55,100 --> 00:14:56,170
What?

216
00:14:58,340 --> 00:15:01,240
Wait, no, that's not what I meant...

217
00:15:03,540 --> 00:15:06,010
I'm getting a call. I have to take this.

218
00:15:10,180 --> 00:15:12,650
Shit. Where's Jang Mi's room?

219
00:15:13,020 --> 00:15:14,180
Aren't you going to take that?

220
00:15:17,890 --> 00:15:19,990
Why are you trying to go
into Tae Pyung's room?

221
00:15:28,470 --> 00:15:30,270
What's gotten into Jang Mi?

222
00:15:31,100 --> 00:15:32,100
Ma Seo Rin!

223
00:15:32,670 --> 00:15:35,770
Why didn't you tell me
your mother is CEO Chae Hwa Young?

224
00:15:35,940 --> 00:15:37,070
So you finally met her.

225
00:15:37,610 --> 00:15:41,110
Don't tell me you marched right in
and started a fight.

226
00:15:42,980 --> 00:15:46,450
Anyway, thank goodness
you are so discerning, Father.

227
00:15:46,780 --> 00:15:49,350
It's a huge relief
you didn't go through with the wedding.

228
00:15:49,750 --> 00:15:53,690
- That's enough.
- I'm very grateful to Father for that.

229
00:16:02,100 --> 00:16:05,100
Tell me what kind of person is CEO Chae.

230
00:16:07,240 --> 00:16:08,740
All right, that's settled then.

231
00:16:08,940 --> 00:16:11,010
Now we just have to keep a close eye
on Seo Rin.

232
00:16:11,640 --> 00:16:13,210
Yes. I'll make sure there are no slip-ups.

233
00:16:15,080 --> 00:16:19,220
She should be grateful
I stole her and not Oh Jang Mi.

234
00:16:19,850 --> 00:16:22,090
I'm the one
who lets her live like a princess.

235
00:16:22,820 --> 00:16:25,920
If I had taken Oh Jang Mi instead of her,

236
00:16:26,760 --> 00:16:28,130
she'd be the one suffering...

237
00:16:28,130 --> 00:16:29,860
as Jung Suk Hee's daughter
right now, right?

238
00:16:30,890 --> 00:16:32,530
She's the person who stole me...

239
00:16:33,230 --> 00:16:34,770
from your mother.

240
00:16:37,470 --> 00:16:38,900
Manager Lee and CEO Chae...

241
00:16:39,900 --> 00:16:41,310
were the ones who stole you?

242
00:16:42,010 --> 00:16:43,010
That's right.

243
00:16:43,270 --> 00:16:44,270
But...

244
00:16:44,580 --> 00:16:46,540
how can you talk about it
like it's someone else's story?

245
00:16:48,310 --> 00:16:49,950
My hands are shaking,

246
00:16:50,080 --> 00:16:52,080
and I'm so furious I can barely breathe.

247
00:16:52,280 --> 00:16:53,420
Calm down.

248
00:16:53,420 --> 00:16:55,750
If she hasn't found you out,
you need to hold it together.

249
00:16:56,120 --> 00:16:59,860
If you lash out now,
you have zero chance of winning.

250
00:17:00,020 --> 00:17:02,060
- What?
- You must realize...

251
00:17:02,060 --> 00:17:03,160
what kind of person my mom is by now.

252
00:17:03,860 --> 00:17:05,330
If she finds out you're Oh Jang Mi,

253
00:17:05,700 --> 00:17:07,260
what do you think my mom will do to you?

254
00:17:22,410 --> 00:17:24,480
- Get over here. Get in, now!
- Somebody help me!

255
00:17:29,120 --> 00:17:30,850
(PC Station)

256
00:17:31,090 --> 00:17:32,090
Jang Mi!

257
00:17:32,420 --> 00:17:33,560
(Mazen PC Station)

258
00:17:43,900 --> 00:17:44,970
Seo Rin.

259
00:17:45,170 --> 00:17:47,240
I'm here. Aren't you coming out to say hi?

260
00:17:48,040 --> 00:17:50,240
What's wrong? Why are you crying?

261
00:17:51,810 --> 00:17:55,250
I can hear her voice.
Jang Mi, listen to me carefully.

262
00:17:55,650 --> 00:17:57,310
Don't get caught.

263
00:17:57,680 --> 00:18:00,950
Ma Seo Rin.
What is it? Why are you crying?

264
00:18:01,250 --> 00:18:02,450
Who are you talking to?

265
00:18:03,950 --> 00:18:04,960
No.

266
00:18:05,190 --> 00:18:06,560
I'm not going to listen to you.

267
00:18:06,620 --> 00:18:08,530
Who are you talking to?

268
00:18:08,890 --> 00:18:09,890
Stop!

269
00:18:10,030 --> 00:18:11,600
You still don't get it
after everything she's done?

270
00:18:11,830 --> 00:18:13,530
If you confront her now,

271
00:18:13,530 --> 00:18:15,600
do you think
she'll admit she's the culprit?

272
00:18:16,400 --> 00:18:18,040
I told you that I have evidence.

273
00:18:18,370 --> 00:18:20,040
Right now, you can't get caught.

274
00:18:20,300 --> 00:18:23,370
Once you have the proof,
you can turn her in yourself.

275
00:18:23,710 --> 00:18:25,240
I have the evidence!

276
00:18:29,110 --> 00:18:31,520
Ma Seo Rin!
What in the world is wrong with you?

277
00:18:31,520 --> 00:18:33,220
Who are you talking to?

278
00:18:33,820 --> 00:18:35,190
Have you been drinking again?

279
00:18:40,190 --> 00:18:41,260
Seo Rin!

280
00:18:41,690 --> 00:18:42,930
Keep your promise.

281
00:18:44,130 --> 00:18:47,130
Ma Seo Rin.
Seriously, what is wrong with you?

282
00:18:47,700 --> 00:18:50,470
Is this another one of your tantrums?
What is it now?

283
00:18:50,700 --> 00:18:52,840
What are you so unhappy about
to treat me this way?

284
00:18:59,210 --> 00:19:00,280
Oh my...

285
00:19:00,510 --> 00:19:03,010
What has gotten into her?
Why is she acting this way?

286
00:19:06,450 --> 00:19:07,550
Is she drunk?

287
00:19:18,830 --> 00:19:21,200
Who could Seo Rin have been talking to?

288
00:19:21,900 --> 00:19:24,000
Why would she suddenly act like that?

289
00:19:25,500 --> 00:19:28,610
Wait, could she have met Oh Jang Mi?

290
00:19:29,540 --> 00:19:30,770
I have a very bad feeling about this.

291
00:19:44,720 --> 00:19:46,860
Hwa Young? Is now a good time?

292
00:19:48,430 --> 00:19:49,930
Yes, it's fine.

293
00:19:51,300 --> 00:19:52,960
After all you've been through,

294
00:19:53,330 --> 00:19:55,400
and I haven't even had a chance
to see you.

295
00:19:56,300 --> 00:19:58,870
It was a bit of a struggle for me,

296
00:19:59,170 --> 00:20:01,570
but thinking of you
helped me get through it.

297
00:20:02,510 --> 00:20:04,610
You were worried sick about me,
weren't you?

298
00:20:05,140 --> 00:20:06,210
Of course.

299
00:20:06,740 --> 00:20:08,750
How could I not be?

300
00:20:09,350 --> 00:20:10,410
But...

301
00:20:10,750 --> 00:20:13,750
that whole thing happened
because you just had a run of bad luck.

302
00:20:14,620 --> 00:20:18,120
So try to forget all about it
and start fresh.

303
00:20:18,890 --> 00:20:20,460
Who is she on the phone with?

304
00:20:21,560 --> 00:20:23,430
What's this about making a fresh start?

305
00:20:25,900 --> 00:20:29,370
There's someone else
behind this case we don't know about.

306
00:20:29,530 --> 00:20:30,700
Not this again?

307
00:20:31,270 --> 00:20:32,500
Someone else is behind it?

308
00:20:32,670 --> 00:20:35,310
Anyway, Mom,
tomorrow afternoon at the office,

309
00:20:35,370 --> 00:20:36,810
let's talk with Jang Mi.

310
00:20:37,170 --> 00:20:40,710
Once you hear what Jang Mi has to say,
you'll understand what I'm talking about.

311
00:20:40,880 --> 00:20:43,950
Why do you keep trying to dredge up a case
that's already been closed?

312
00:20:44,180 --> 00:20:45,650
I just don't understand.

313
00:20:46,180 --> 00:20:47,420
Mom, please.

314
00:20:47,680 --> 00:20:48,690
Fine.

315
00:20:49,020 --> 00:20:52,090
I'll meet this Oh Jang Mi
that I've heard so much about.

316
00:20:52,990 --> 00:20:55,160
Come to think of it, I've never seen her.

317
00:20:55,160 --> 00:20:56,630
I've heard so much about her.

318
00:21:01,770 --> 00:21:03,070
- Goodness, honey.
- What?

319
00:21:03,070 --> 00:21:05,140
Where are you going at this hour?

320
00:21:05,700 --> 00:21:09,740
I've been cooped up at home and feel
out of the loop with the university.

321
00:21:11,140 --> 00:21:12,540
So you're meeting with the professors.

322
00:21:13,440 --> 00:21:17,550
That's good.
You should get out and see people.

323
00:21:18,220 --> 00:21:20,250
- See you later, Dad.
- Okay, son.

324
00:21:20,320 --> 00:21:21,420
Oh, honey.

325
00:21:23,290 --> 00:21:26,620
Have a good time and don't drink too much.

326
00:21:26,720 --> 00:21:28,160
Gosh, seriously...

327
00:21:28,160 --> 00:21:29,290
Alright.

328
00:21:31,230 --> 00:21:33,430
He's just putting on a show.
I know he likes it.

329
00:21:34,870 --> 00:21:36,300
My eyes hurt.

330
00:21:48,710 --> 00:21:51,750
(Do I have a twin?)

331
00:22:10,330 --> 00:22:15,470
(Oh Jang Mi)

332
00:22:18,680 --> 00:22:20,840
Something's definitely off with Seo Rin.

333
00:22:22,380 --> 00:22:25,650
I'm terrified Oh Jang Mi might meet her.

334
00:22:27,320 --> 00:22:28,350
Oh Jang Mi.

335
00:22:29,350 --> 00:22:31,250
I need to get rid of her quickly.

336
00:22:33,160 --> 00:22:34,760
(Oh Jang Mi)

337
00:22:57,250 --> 00:22:58,620
(CEO Chae Hwa Young)

338
00:22:59,550 --> 00:23:01,650
- Yes, ma'am.
- Kang Hyuk.

339
00:23:02,420 --> 00:23:04,350
You've got men watching
Oh Jang Mi's place, right?

340
00:23:05,060 --> 00:23:07,320
- Yes.
- That's not good enough.

341
00:23:08,130 --> 00:23:10,660
I'd rather eliminate
any potential threats.

342
00:23:11,500 --> 00:23:14,060
Take care of her tomorrow.

343
00:23:15,400 --> 00:23:16,900
I understand perfectly.

344
00:23:17,700 --> 00:23:19,170
I’ll take care of what you asked
first thing tomorrow.

345
00:23:30,950 --> 00:23:32,750
Oh Jang Mi's D-Day is tomorrow.

346
00:23:33,280 --> 00:23:36,750
Understood. I'll make sure it's done.

347
00:23:48,100 --> 00:23:50,730
Dad, this is the CEO who's sponsoring me.

348
00:23:50,970 --> 00:23:52,900
She's the one who helped me
get my recent gig.

349
00:23:53,500 --> 00:23:54,810
About the banner.

350
00:23:54,810 --> 00:23:56,610
If I remember correctly,
she also filed a complaint...

351
00:23:56,670 --> 00:23:58,340
to have a banner taken down.

352
00:24:00,080 --> 00:24:02,580
She pretended to be a good person
to get close to my family...

353
00:24:02,950 --> 00:24:04,210
so she could spy on us.

354
00:24:04,820 --> 00:24:06,880
That's why she had the witness banner
taken down...

355
00:24:07,380 --> 00:24:09,590
and offered to send me to the US
to get rid of me.

356
00:24:10,820 --> 00:24:13,220
Chae Hwa Young, you horrible woman.

357
00:24:14,120 --> 00:24:16,560
I'm going to the police right now
and make her pay for what she's done.

358
00:24:17,230 --> 00:24:18,300
I won't let her get away with this.

359
00:24:25,970 --> 00:24:26,970
Jang Mi.

360
00:24:27,370 --> 00:24:28,910
Close up the store tonight.

361
00:24:33,110 --> 00:24:36,410
Close up? More like,
Oh Jang Mi's life will come to a close.

362
00:24:40,720 --> 00:24:42,550
Hey. Where are you?

363
00:24:43,250 --> 00:24:45,620
A playground? Where's that?

364
00:24:47,090 --> 00:24:49,630
It's fine. I'll look up the location
and come to you,

365
00:24:49,760 --> 00:24:50,760
so just stay there.

366
00:24:50,760 --> 00:24:52,630
Don't bother coming here...

367
00:24:52,730 --> 00:24:54,630
and risk my mom or anyone else seeing you.

368
00:24:54,760 --> 00:24:56,030
Just wait for me right there.

369
00:25:01,270 --> 00:25:03,270
I said I'm going, so just wait!

370
00:25:05,780 --> 00:25:07,340
Jang Mi, are you mad at me?

371
00:25:09,180 --> 00:25:10,950
Is that why you were avoiding me earlier?

372
00:25:13,220 --> 00:25:14,350
Are you really mad?

373
00:25:14,850 --> 00:25:17,020
- The settlement agreement?
- What?

374
00:25:18,560 --> 00:25:21,390
- Jang Mi.
- Just say it. I'm not deaf.

375
00:25:22,730 --> 00:25:24,060
I understand why you're upset.

376
00:25:24,760 --> 00:25:28,130
But my mom isn't the type of person
to just throw money at problems.

377
00:25:28,300 --> 00:25:30,270
- But...
- Why not use money to fix things?

378
00:25:30,470 --> 00:25:32,500
Is there anything in this world
that money can't solve?

379
00:25:32,970 --> 00:25:34,000
Go on, name one.

380
00:25:34,770 --> 00:25:36,140
I understand how you feel.

381
00:25:37,270 --> 00:25:39,240
What can I do to make it up to you?

382
00:25:39,940 --> 00:25:42,450
Will you grant me a wish?

383
00:25:45,150 --> 00:25:47,250
I never knew you had
this side to you, Jang Mi.

384
00:25:47,380 --> 00:25:48,690
Don't change the subject.

385
00:25:49,320 --> 00:25:50,920
Right.

386
00:25:51,290 --> 00:25:53,760
- I'll do whatever you want.
- Okay.

387
00:25:54,560 --> 00:25:56,290
I'll think about it and give you a call.

388
00:25:57,260 --> 00:25:58,260
Hello?

389
00:26:01,560 --> 00:26:02,870
She seems really mad.

390
00:26:04,230 --> 00:26:07,500
Maybe that's why, but something
about the way she talked seems off.

391
00:26:10,640 --> 00:26:13,410
I wonder what Jun Ho is doing right now.

392
00:26:13,940 --> 00:26:14,950
I miss him.

393
00:26:17,050 --> 00:26:18,620
I can't be wasting time like this.

394
00:26:19,380 --> 00:26:20,380
I should go.

395
00:26:46,240 --> 00:26:48,450
- Give me the evidence.
- I don't have it with me.

396
00:26:48,450 --> 00:26:50,050
You said you'd give me the evidence!

397
00:26:50,680 --> 00:26:53,250
Do you even have any evidence?

398
00:26:53,250 --> 00:26:54,580
Of course I do.

399
00:26:54,750 --> 00:26:56,850
That's why I you stay with my mother.

400
00:26:57,820 --> 00:27:02,060
I can't be the one to turn in
the woman who raised me.

401
00:27:04,390 --> 00:27:06,360
Don't you trust me?

402
00:27:07,100 --> 00:27:09,970
This isn't just about you, it's about me.

403
00:27:10,170 --> 00:27:11,870
If I hadn't felt like this was my fight,

404
00:27:11,870 --> 00:27:14,070
I wouldn't have even bothered
showing up in the first place.

405
00:27:14,470 --> 00:27:18,040
And I certainly wouldn't have done
this whole one-day switch.

406
00:27:18,240 --> 00:27:19,680
Why would I take such a risk?

407
00:27:21,010 --> 00:27:22,610
I did it because I was afraid
you'd get killed.

408
00:27:25,150 --> 00:27:27,350
Did you meet my mother?

409
00:27:28,120 --> 00:27:30,620
She was always going on and on
about Tok Hee.

410
00:27:32,720 --> 00:27:33,960
It's Ok Hee and Tok Hee!

411
00:27:37,160 --> 00:27:38,860
I followed Tok Hee.

412
00:27:41,260 --> 00:27:43,170
Suk Hee's daughters, Ok Hee and Tok Hee.

413
00:27:43,970 --> 00:27:45,200
You're my daughters.

414
00:27:47,840 --> 00:27:48,840
Mom.

415
00:27:49,910 --> 00:27:51,240
We're reunited!

416
00:27:51,240 --> 00:27:52,940
Suk Hee's daughters, Ok Hee and Tok Hee.

417
00:27:53,010 --> 00:27:54,680
I met Ok Hee and Tok Hee.

418
00:27:56,050 --> 00:27:57,210
We're together!

419
00:28:33,580 --> 00:28:34,950
(The First Man)

420
00:28:35,020 --> 00:28:36,890
Find her now!

421
00:28:37,220 --> 00:28:39,790
Who in the world was she talking to?

422
00:28:39,990 --> 00:28:42,360
Seo Rin was acting so strange today.

423
00:28:42,690 --> 00:28:44,830
Jang Mi, I'll protect you.

424
00:28:45,330 --> 00:28:47,500
I'm sorry, and I love you, Jang Mi.

425
00:28:48,000 --> 00:28:51,370
Why did she write my name
in today's date box and then erase it?

426
00:28:51,730 --> 00:28:53,000
What could that mean?

427
00:28:53,000 --> 00:28:55,840
Chae Hwa Young. What are you scheming now?

428
00:28:59,210 --> 00:29:01,210
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
